<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98448885824601></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98448885824601><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=7&mid=98448885824601>RE: Nuke/Melee Clerics</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=7&mid=98448885824601#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Mar 13th 8:07 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>i beg to differ.&nbsp;&nbsp;just let me warn every cleric that reads this page of one thing.  clerics, druids, and shammies that melee at higher levels--meaning 30 and up basically--get put on peoples lists.<br><br>everyone hates casters that melee.  the do too little damage for it to be worth while, and on top of that, they are NOT MEDDING.  <br><br>example, we had to wait for a druid the other night to sow us because he was in melee.  everyone in the group started saying "SIT DOWN AND MED."   the tanks asked for nukes from the druid, "I am LOM" was the response as he stood there wakking away for 8points of a damage an attack.<br><br>BAH! don't melee as a caster, then you need to be healed on top of it.  more mana drain on the main healer.  2 clerics in a group can be evil.  chain stunning mobs is sweet stuff.<br><br>please don't listen to other people who say clerics should melee, they are wrong, and you will be punished later for it trust me.  people make lists.<br><br>have you ever heard someone say in a group, "what is the name of the bard coming?"  that is because they have a list of people they won't group with.  i do.  most people have them at higher levels.  you don't want to get on one of these lists.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
