	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>So in your opinion all a cleric can do is heal/buff?&nbsp;&nbsp;Hmmmmm.... Okay..  If you say so....  When I melee I use spells like a Wizzie more than anything.... Especially Banish Undead and retribution.  <br><br>As to being put on lists... Yes I have been put on many lists...  Recieving many tells to group with... Because I will heal and can do some melee or DD casting.... (In other words Good Lists) I do agree as a rule too little DMG is doled out by a cleric in straight combat....  Leave that to the warriors.<br><br>Face it.....  How many Bad players make it past level 30, let alone level 40?  So I must be doing something right along with everyone else who plays their characters to the fullest.  the game is meant to be fun and you should enjoy everything you can about the character class and race you choose...  I have a lot of fun playing as I do and don't have any complaints or a lot of people dying because I am meleeing instead of healing...  like I said in other post  ALWAYS make SURE you have MANA and WATCH HP BARS for whole group.<br><br>Play your character the way you wish to play it and what works best for you....  all any of us here can do is relete our experiences from playing these characters.  <br><br>I used to think I was doing really well till I met some really terrific Clerics and People in my current guild.  They have collectively and individually shown me so much in a very short time.  Hats Off to all You Shadow Lords and Ladies.....  Your guidence and knowledge have helped so much more than you will ever know....<br><br>Eannyil Rezzuwell<br>44th cleric <br>Of the Shadow Order<br>Lanys<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
